<h2>Who we are</h2>

<p>The event is put together by
<a href="http://openhatch.org/people/paulproteus/">Asheesh Laroia</a>,
<a href="http://openhatch.org/people/ymasory/">Yuvi Masory</a>, and <a href="http://github.com/fford">Felice Ford</a> with the generous help of the Penn Department of Computer and Information Science. Asheesh hopes
